hopobject.body: What's the interest rate on this account? hingham centre pharmacy hours More than 30 boat arrivals have been involved. The majority have come from Egypt, although some started their journeys from Turkey. Most of the arrivals have been families with children. Several people have needed hospital treatment for dehydration, and there have been instances of people having to be airlifted directly from the boat they were traveling on.
